S[outh African science fiction novel “Zoo City”
](http://blogs.indiewire.com/shadowandact/south-african-sci-fi-novelist-
lauren-beukes-zoo-city-to-get-film-adaptation)will soon be a movie: “After
winning several literary awards and garnering global acclaim for its clever
originality, South African author Lauren Beukes’ science-fiction novel, Zoo
City, recently saw its film rights awarded to producer Helena Spring (Red
Dust, Yesterday, The First Grader), a fellow South African.”

